title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“No one can really know which side of the fence McKinnon is straddling.” [From The West Palm Beach Post, 9 June 1984. Submitted by J. B. Lawrence, San Bernardino, California.]
